{"article_id":"YyxW9yHon3kHKHCb","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"President Trump said Friday","depth":4},{"id":1,"text":"that the U.S. is again talking with North Korean officials ,","depth":5},{"id":2,"text":"a day after he canceled a June 12 denuclearization summit due to Pyongyang ' s \" hostility \" toward his administration .","depth":5},{"id":3,"text":"\" We ' re talking to them now , \"","depth":5},{"id":4,"text":"Mr. Trump told reporters at the White House .","depth":5},{"id":5,"text":"\" They very much want to do it .","depth":6},{"id":6,"text":"We ' d like to do it .","depth":6},{"id":7,"text":"We ' ll see what happens . \"","depth":5},{"id":8,"text":"The White House even left open the possibility Friday","depth":5},{"id":9,"text":"of dispatching a summit planning team to Singapore","depth":5},{"id":10,"text":"if the meeting is rescheduled .","depth":4},{"id":11,"text":"\" There are still a few hours left","depth":6},{"id":12,"text":"to decide , \"","depth":6},{"id":13,"text":"White House press secretary Sarah Huckabee Sanders told reporters .","depth":5},{"id":14,"text":"\" If it takes place on June 12 ,","depth":6},{"id":15,"text":"we ' ll be ready .","depth":6},{"id":16,"text":"If it takes place on July 12 ,","depth":6},{"id":17,"text":"we ' ll be ready . \"","depth":6},{"id":18,"text":"Mr. Trump said","depth":5},{"id":19,"text":"North Korea released a \" very nice statement \" in response to his canceling the summit in Singapore .","depth":6},{"id":20,"text":"He said","depth":7},{"id":21,"text":"the meeting could even be put back on track for June 12 .","depth":7},{"id":22,"text":"In a statement Thursday night , a top North Korean official expressed Pyongyang ' s willingness","depth":6},{"id":23,"text":"to meet with Mr. Trump \" anytime and in any format. \"","depth":6},{"id":24,"text":"The statement said","depth":6},{"id":25,"text":"North Korea is \" open-minded in giving time and opportunity to the U.S . \"","depth":6},{"id":26,"text":"Secretary of State Mike Pompeo said Thursday","depth":5},{"id":27,"text":"that North Korean officials had stopped communicating with U.S. officials in recent days .","depth":5},{"id":28,"text":"The White House also said","depth":5},{"id":29,"text":"that North Korea stood up a U.S. advance team in Singapore last week for a meeting","depth":6},{"id":30,"text":"that was intended to work on preparations for the June 12 summit .","depth":6},{"id":31,"text":"Asked if North Korea is playing games ,","depth":4},{"id":32,"text":"Mr. Trump said ,","depth":5},{"id":33,"text":"\" Everybody plays games .","depth":6},{"id":34,"text":"You know that better than anybody . \"","depth":6},{"id":35,"text":"Sen. Lindsey Graham , South Carolina Republican , said","depth":6},{"id":36,"text":"he spoke with Mr. Trump on Thursday ,","depth":7},{"id":37,"text":"and the president feels","depth":8},{"id":38,"text":"as if North Korea was trying to manipulate him .","depth":8},{"id":39,"text":"\" The president feels","depth":8},{"id":40,"text":"like","depth":9},{"id":41,"text":"they ' re playing him ,","depth":9},{"id":42,"text":"so he brought it to an end ,","depth":8},{"id":43,"text":"and we ' ll see","depth":9},{"id":44,"text":"if we can reengage , \"","depth":9},{"id":45,"text":"Mr. Graham told radio host Hugh Hewitt .","depth":6},{"id":46,"text":"\" I personally believe ,","depth":7},{"id":47,"text":"having talked to the president as of yesterday ,","depth":7},{"id":48,"text":"that he ' s going to bring this to conclusion in his first term .","depth":6},{"id":49,"text":"He ' s made a decision","depth":7},{"id":50,"text":"to end the North Korean nuclear program .","depth":7},{"id":51,"text":"He wants to do it peacefully ,","depth":7},{"id":52,"text":"if possible . \"","depth":7}],"relations":[{"parent":105,"left":70,"right":104,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":70,"left":60,"right":69,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":60,"left":55,"right":59,"relation":"elaboration","nuclear